AcknowledgeMessage.name: AcknowledgeMessage
AcknowledgeMessage.description: Acknowledges a message, ensuring it will not be delivered again

FailMessage.name: FailMessage
FailMessage.description:
Fails a message, signifying the message could not be processed successfully, ensuring
                                                it cannot be replied to or delivered again

GetEndpoint.name: GetEndpoint
GetEndpoint.description: Routes traffic to the correct endpoint based on the given destination for the messages

GetMessages.name: GetMessages
GetMessages.description: Delivers messages to clients/instances using long polling

SendReply.name: SendReply
SendReply.description: Sends replies from clients/instances to upstream service
